{
  "stem": "7873.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Once you got out of the barrack, you were never allowed to see the-- till late at night, to, to go in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Doesn't matter if it's fires, flood, anything, you cannot go in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they give you a little bit of some kind-- ersatz coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So half of it, you washed your face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And half of it, you dranked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here I hear a commotion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A friend of mine, we went to cheder together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He walks out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they accused him that he was inside already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He took-- that already, he took bread twice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could never go back inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But what they'd do, these guys used to steal from us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they accused you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You were taking twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they killed the guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, anyway, the kid started crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I wasn't inside any-- I wasn't-- the second time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I never did twice-- taken bread twice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, one hollers to the other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They're starting to beat that kid over the head till he fell in the mud.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Mud wasn't that-- Birkenau had mud up to your knees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sometimes, you left your shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You couldn't pull, pull your feet up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The shoes got lost in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Till he fell into the mud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Once you fell into the mud-- they used to carry sticks with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They put the stick on his neck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One guy stepped on one side, the other guy stepped on the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's the first-- the first casualty I see, what they did to a person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Till that kid died, stick his tongue out, choked himself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I remember it was a weekend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Every day used to come shipments with people-- every day, every day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We-- I was already assigned to a Barrack 8.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
